{"tid":610987,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[You can't beat him, buy him] 外國傳媒報導香港足總有意斟介北韓主教練","createTime":"2018-03-30T13:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T09:26:17.000Z","uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"617adf7a97267ab6077f778de00d813952d457c2","tid":610987,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"北韓主教練安達臣已在帶領北韓殺入亞洲盃決賽周後離任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rbnett.no/ntb/sport/2018/03/28/TV-2-J%C3%B8rn-Andersen-aktuell-for-Hongkong-16383826.ece\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbnett.no%2Fntb%2Fsport%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2FTV-2-J%25C3%25B8rn-Andersen-aktuell-for-Hongkong-16383826.ece&d=5uhCr9pl1eHD9o0NWXfhURFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=3226e33e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rbnett.no/ntb/sport/2018/03/28/TV-2-J%C3%B8rn-Andersen-aktuell-for-Hongkong-16383826.ece</a>"},{"pid":"8df2532e610e438b6da30b2f7ca1cca84125f0d0","tid":610987,"uid":66314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:04:55.000Z","msg":"金仔派過嚟嘅臥底"},{"pid":"4bdfe57c43b48edaa526918024b1efb11b4e4e1b","tid":610987,"uid":44268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"睇嚟想拎香港做跳板北上喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d579d98623c74716875218db69ea4ac6f97d90","tid":610987,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4bdfe57c43b48edaa526918024b1efb11b4e4e1b","tid":610987,"uid":44268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"睇嚟想拎香港做跳板北上喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"咁既CV肯黎唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112aecbba57d66b8d37b14990853ab1716d84927","tid":610987,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"薛基輔讚朝鮮男足主帥 挪威TV2解讀：有機會成下任港足主教練<br />\n<br />\n香港足球代表隊在周二（3月27日）戰罷亞洲盃外圍賽最後一輪比賽後，今年上半年暫未有比賽計劃，最快要到9月的國際賽期才有比賽，按此前部署香港足總將趁這段空檔招聘新任港足主教練，而足總行政總裁薛基輔本周接受挪威TV2電視台訪問時讚賞朝鮮男足主帥安達臣（Jorn Andersen），TV2在報道就解讀稱該名德甲前金靴有可能成為下任港足主帥。<br />\n<br />\nTV2本周的一篇報道，近日獲數個挪威媒體轉載，報道稱周二之戰最後領軍朝鮮的安達臣「接近成為香港代表隊新任主帥」。報道內容稱，安達臣與數名香港球員有過交流，而薛基輔接受TV2訪問時也稱：「我們看過朝鮮隊作客香港的比賽了，感覺他（安達臣）態度專業、待人友善，朝鮮球員看起來狀態很好，而且技術出色，證明他的工作做得出色。」<br />\n<br />\n訪問片段中，薛基輔未有提及有關下任港足主帥的事，而按其此前接受本網訪問時所言，亞盃外之後將招聘港足新主帥，接替去年底辭職的金判坤，而TV2在報道就稱安達臣有可能是人選，安達臣向TV2表示：「現在言之尚早，我知道香港足總有興趣與我談談，也只是剛聽到他們在物色新主帥。現在我可是市場上可供選擇的人。」"},{"pid":"52158efc578eaf5c27e4575b53e04b1c8409087f","tid":610987,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"一齊DIE FOR HONG KONG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e255640cd48fa010a854de806b8c2e1c3e9c482","tid":610987,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"係就快啦CEO"},{"pid":"5dbcba5e36c82d05dee87edaa9d015b69b7dab00","tid":610987,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f120d201d8eec29a24080623390bc0ba62a107d8","tid":610987,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e255640cd48fa010a854de806b8c2e1c3e9c482","tid":610987,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"係就快啦CEO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}